# UX Reliability Gates

## Checkout UX Safety

- Never silently fail checkout steps.
- Show actionable error states with recovery action (retry, edit address, pick another slot).
- If address/fulfillment/slot changes, force fee and availability revalidation.

## Form and Validation Safety

- Use `react-hook-form` + `zod` for customer/admin forms.
- Validate on server even if client-side validation exists.
- Keep customer input when possible after recoverable failures.

## Performance and Stability

- Avoid blocking UI on non-critical requests.
- Use loading/skeleton states for async checkout and status steps.
- Ensure mobile-first interactions remain usable with one-hand flow.

## Accessibility Baseline

- Label all interactive controls and form fields.
- Ensure keyboard and screen-reader path works for checkout completion.
